      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SCOTT ENIGMA (1) well back settling but did wind up strongly to finish 4th and beaten only 2.25 lengths (19.66) at Bulli. Remains without a win from the draw but has been in the placings two times from three attempts. Better than last start and worth following up. ZIPPING LOMBARDI (5) ran above expectations last time to win her first race by a neck at this track over 400m (23.72). Has two placings this course. Leading player again. SCOTT ELYSIAN (8) produced a moderate run last time when seventh at Bulli over 340m behind Siam High (20.23) in a Grade 5. Must be included in calculations. INDIGO PEARL (2) can return to form after missing the top-three at this circuit last time out.",
